  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brace for enemies, prepare for mania! <strong>Enemania</strong> is a thrilling tower defense game that pits you against hordes of monstrous enemies. As waves of skeletons, orcs, zombies, mummies, and knights charge towards your treasure, you must strategically place and upgrade your weapons to repel their attacks. With a diverse arsenal of cannons, catapults, and bombs at your disposal, you'll need to think quickly and adapt to each level's unique challenges. Can you withstand the onslaught and emerge victorious? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403610/extras/8cb0b61c0c4b84dd3900643c04ef9152.avif?t=1740746096\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403610/extras_big/8cb0b61c0c4b84dd3900643c04ef9152.avif?t=1740746096 width=800 height=571 /></span></p>",
